sources.description:
It's Friday@PizzaFLIX 
Stars: Rue McClanahan, Paul Leder, King Moody
Director: John Hayes

When their car breaks down en route to San Diego, a young family is forced to take a detour. They soon find themselves stranded at a backwoods junkyard and in the clutches of a seedy racketeer.
